- New enemy: the Maple. Track and hunt Maples in the sector map to earn Credits!
- Use Credits to purchase the new PAC-MAN ship and more
- PAC-MAN ship available with 4 new special abilities, new enemy visuals and new sector backgrounds
- You can now purchase coin packs
- Twin ship and abilities now last through hyperspace
- Daily mission timer and progress bar visible on the main menu for easier tracking
- Sector score multiplier is now visible in the warp sector map

New ship available! Fly as the Red Baron from the 80's Namco classic Sky Kid!

Every extra ship you own now gives you an extra life during gameplay and reduces all ship upgrade costs by 10%!

All previous ships in the store can now also be purchased with Credits!

The game now supports relative touch controls! You can change your control preference in the settings menu.
